conversations.original_question: Patient: Linda Harris, Age: 54, SSN: 159-75-3486, Address: 147 Birch Road. By the way, if i lay down or sit down, my head do not spin, only when i want to move around then i feel the whole world is spinning.. And it is normal stomach discomfort at the same time? Earlier after i relieved myself, the spinning lessen so i am not sure whether its connected or coincidences.. Thank you doc!
